# Gemini CLI Environment Configuration

This environment uses a standard Gemini CLI setup managed via **chezmoi**.

## Management & Source of Truth

Configuration is managed as a set of dotfiles. Changes must be made in the source repository and applied using `chezmoi apply`.

- **Source Directory:** `~/.local/share/chezmoi/dot_gemini/`
- **Active Configuration:** `~/.gemini/`

## Extension Mechanisms

We utilize the standard Gemini CLI extension tiers. For detailed documentation on how to author these, refer to the [Gemini CLI Skills Documentation](https://gemini.google.com/cli/docs/skills).

### Custom Commands
- **Source:** `~/.local/share/chezmoi/dot_gemini/commands/*.toml.tmpl`
- **Active:** `~/.gemini/commands/`

### Agent Skills
- **Source:** `~/.local/share/chezmoi/dot_gemini/skills/`
- **Active:** `~/.gemini/skills/`

## Behavioral Mandates

Core behavioral rules are composed from shared templates in `.chezmoitemplates/` and rendered into `~/.gemini/GEMINI.md`.
